From: "Alan Dershowitz" 
To: 
Subject:From an ers rowrtz 
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2009 15:59:26 +0000 
Importance: Normal 
Dear 
Sony I didn't get back to you sooner but I've been incredibly busy since I left paradise in Miami Beach. Just 
argued an appeal in NY and debated the Mideast at Georgetown. I greatly appreciate your willingness to call the 
sheriff and advise him that your office would take no position on how he handled Epstein's sentence as long as 
he didn't get special treatment, but let's put any call off for a while. . Thanks. 
Alan 
EFTA00013605
